<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA16">
<l>iṉiyō nāmuyntō miṟaiva ṉaruḷcērntō</l>
<l>miṉiyō riṭarillō neñcē - yiṉiyōr</l>
<l>viṉaikkaṭalai yākkuvikku mīḷāp piṟavik</l>
<l>kaṉaikkaṭalai nīntiṉōṅ kāṇ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Have we escaped now? We have joined the grace of the lord.</l>
<l>Now we are without affliction, heart. Now we have swum, see,</l>
<l>the thundering ocean of birth without returning</l>
<l>that creates an ocean of karma.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
